{"tid":2121241,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做人好攰","createTime":"2020-07-23T07:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T03:22:33.000Z","uid":78243,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"25933630a1ab283aa31cc53308b662085e99a0aa","tid":2121241,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0294f85b71a0d9af82f3419288a20f2e96334f0","tid":2121241,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:49:16.000Z","msg":"死"},{"pid":"5b2a76e11276ce8eab481135bc0c14a675ba365b","tid":2121241,"uid":78243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:50:33.000Z","msg":"身心都好攰﹐就到極根"},{"pid":"1be77576007234b444fe2d973a4b53172ba128d5","tid":2121241,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:54:55.000Z","msg":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。<br />\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline</a>"},{"pid":"2bf33f46b54a89ea8bcf366043c4f471321af49f","tid":2121241,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:55:19.000Z","msg":"看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，到我們的網站 <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=53874bb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a> 。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（ <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=1fd40e01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php</a> ）。 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"4b51679c4618aa18c81414dc7d73529f2d74c736","tid":2121241,"uid":149981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:03:41.000Z","msg":"點樣攰法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講嚟聽吓"},{"pid":"639b2bcd80337db5e7c89ec477bed523ef64d81c","tid":2121241,"uid":36248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"做愛囉"},{"pid":"ceab899abcd56e5a32541d0d40453df02eaa331f","tid":2121241,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"搵多d興趣做，識多d人，睇多d電視節目"},{"pid":"901e258919baef2e8932db17fbf094cea7d3a747","tid":2121241,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b51679c4618aa18c81414dc7d73529f2d74c736","tid":2121241,"uid":149981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:03:41.000Z","msg":"點樣攰法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講嚟聽吓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"健康：成日都覺得訓唔夠，一日叫攰叫到黑<br />\n工作：人工係我朋友之中最低，又無得放假又無得去旅行<br />\n感情：成日見到暗戀既人post ig, 又知道就算我搵佢地唔會應我<br />\n仲要個人無目標，日日行屍走肉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e707ad23d048de383f40d48ab6791dfeff63a5","tid":2121241,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ceab899abcd56e5a32541d0d40453df02eaa331f","tid":2121241,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"搵多d興趣做，識多d人，睇多d電視節目"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:57:57.000Z","msg":"點識人，而家咩活動都停哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85df21f2ac6b4b6dcd7139d3b5f971a542bc0256","tid":2121241,"uid